column5: I live in  Niagara and love musky fishing. I have found some cool places to fish them and would like some company. I don't have a boat so I fish from shore.I fish ALLOT of carp to.   Jeff
Try posting int he 'Hook Ups' forum, Jeff I'm in Niagara but on the DL for a few more weeks.
ya dumb damn, all u have to do is call

PM me your phone # I talked to Darrel last night at the river and forgot to ask him for your #. I will go Monday if you want to go.The moon phases are lining up. I saw 2 fish in the 45"-50" range by your house  :o   JW
I PM'd you. I'm always looking for new people to fish with!
i sent u a PM man, PM me back with a number and we will try and hook up for a few casts!

Theres been a bunch of little ones getting caught right now, also there was a MONSTER pulled from our uber secret winter fishing hole or in the area anyways. Ill shoot u my number man make sure you use it. Been trying for salmon alot lately you should come on out
Hellfish I am going at first light on Tuesday If you want to go call me.   JW
